// Conditional Rendering = isme components,text,element ko render krne wale h, basis of some conditions.



Example:- 
1. if my age is < 18 then i will not ready for vote, but more than 18 then i will.

2. agr user logged in h, to usko logout k button dikhega
if login ni h, to login k

to y hota conditions statement

** 4 Varients hote h:-

1. conditions operator
2. ternary operator
3. logical operator
4. Early return

    // 1. if - else


Example:-
if(isLoggedIn) {
    return (
    <LogoutBtn />
    )  
}
else {
    return(
        <LoginBtn />
    )
}

2. ternary operator           =

Example:-
{isLoggedIn ? <LogoutBtn /> : <LoginBtn />}



3. logical operator           = yha p condtions h, ki koye agr loggedIn h, to bs logedout k button dikhna h, simple.

Example:-
{isLoggedIn && <LogoutBtn />}

agr isloggedin and (&&) y operator apne laga rakhi h, to aap loggedoutBtn dikhna chahte h.


4. Early return               = agr koye condition k adahr pa "UI" dikhn h, oo apne phle hi dikha diya.



Example:-